com.salesforce.androidsdk.analytics.store

Class EventStoreManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.androidsdk.analytics.store.EventStoreManager

  • public class EventStoreManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides APIs to store events in an encrypted store on the filesystem. Each event is stored in a separate file on the filesystem.
    Author:
    bhariharan
